# Build On Flow

Flow is a fast, decentralized platform for apps, games, and digital assets. Build and grow your projects on a scalable, secure network. Whether you're learning Cadence or using EVM compatibility, Flow empowers your innovative ideas.[Get Building](/build/getting-started/contract-interaction)![](/assets/images/landing-home-0aaf60121003a50588089dfa40fe3122.png)Key FeaturesDiscover the innovative features that make Flow the blockchain built for the next generation of apps, games, and digital assets.
